  "keyFeatures": [
    "Show native incoming call UI on Android and iOS (CallKit)",
    "Start and manage outgoing calls",
    "Full call lifecycle events (accept, decline, end, timeout, hold, mute)",
    "VoIP PushKit integration for iOS background wake",
    "Missed call and calling notification support on Android",
    "Custom Android UI with background image, ringtone, and colors",
    "Native Swift/Kotlin integration for call initiation from platform code",
    "Android 13+ notification permission and Android 14+ full-screen intent support"
